attributes.Long form description: The student looks at the different parts of the furniture. The student then starts to put the furniture together by attaching the legs to the shelf. The student then attaches the top shelf to the legs. The student then tightens all the screws on the furniture.

attributes.Transcription: All right now please assemble it.

attributes.Action sentence: The student inspects the top table, shelf, and legs.
The student assembles the first leg on the shelf.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student has to screw it with the allen wrench.

attributes.Transcription: Put it right here, on the table.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student has to grab the Allen wrench.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student should not screw the screws too much.

attributes.Transcription: You don't have to tie it to everything till they are into all the screws. Just make sure that won't fall down.

attributes.Action sentence: The student assembles the second leg of the shelf.
The student assembles the third leg on the shelf.
The student assembles the fourth leg of the shelf.
The student assembles the top shelf of the furniture.
The student puts the remaining screws onto the top table.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student should put lay down to it, to put.

attributes.Transcription: Maybe you can put lay down to it, to put.

attributes.Action sentence: The student tightens the screws on the furniture.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student drops the hex socket head.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student must move the leg to the edge of the table so he can screw it.

attributes.Transcription: You can move it to the bank of the table.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student accidentally drop the allen wrench.
